## Category Mapping
- áo, áo sơ mi, áo khoác, shirt -> Shirts
- quần, quần dài, quần short, pants -> Pants
- balo, ba lô, backpack -> Backpacks
- dao, dụng cụ, đồ camping -> Camping Tools
- lều, trại, tent -> Tents
- mũ, nón, hat -> Hats
- bếp, stove, grill -> Cooking Equipment

## Color Mapping
- đen, màu đen, black -> Black
- đỏ, màu đỏ, red -> Red
- xanh, xanh dương, blue -> Blue

## Size Mapping
- size s, s -> S
- size m, m -> M
- size l, l -> L
- size small, small -> small
- size big, big -> big

## Feature Mapping
- chống nắng, chống uv, uv, uv protection, sun protection, omni-shade -> UV
- nhanh khô, quick dry, quick-dry, omni-wick -> quick-dry
- chống nước, waterproof, water resistant -> waterproof
- trekking, leo núi, hiking, outdoor, camping, mountaineering -> trekking
- siêu nhẹ, lightweight, ultralight -> lightweight

## Database Reality Notes
- Pants strongly match: waterproof, quick-dry, trekking, lightweight, UV
- Shirts strongly match: quick-dry, UV
- Backpacks strongly match: lightweight, hiking, mountaineering
- Tents strongly match: trekking, camping, outdoor
- Hats strongly match: UV, quick-dry
- Cooking Equipment strongly match: camping, outdoor, stove, grill
- Shirts currently do not strongly support waterproof queries
- Tents and Camping Tools usually do not use color/size filters in current DB